{"storyMeta":{"storyReviewType":"NONE","storyId":"act11d0_level_act11d0_sub-1-2_end","storyGroup":"act11d0","storySort":20,"storyDependence":"act11d0_level_act11d0_sub-1-1_end","storyCanShow":1,"storyCode":"TW-S-2","storyName":"一束哀悼","storyPic":null,"storyInfo":"在火灾现场，亚叶与铃兰遇见了同样前来献花的泥岩。所有人都希望能阻止什么，所有人都没能做到。","storyCanEnter":1,"storyTxt":"activities/act11d0/level_act11d0_sub-1-2_end","avgTag":"行动后","unLockType":"STAGE_CLEAR","costItemType":"NONE","costItemId":null,"costItemCount":0,"stageCount":1,"requiredStages":[{"stageId":"act11d0_s02","minState":"PASS","maxState":"COMPLETE"}],"prev":18,"characters":["萨卡兹战士","泥岩","武装的感染者","灰喉","亚叶"]},"lines":[{"type":"header","key":"title_test","skippable":"true","mode":"BLACK_MASK","text":"九尾狐活动 支线2","id":0},{"type":"stopmusic","id":1},{"type":"dialog","id":2},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":3},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":4},{"type":"background","image":"https://prts.wiki/images/8/80/Avg_bg_bg_ltstrongpoint.png","screenadapt":"coverall","id":5},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":6},{"type":"playmusic","intro":"$drift_intro","key":"https://static.prts.wiki/music/music/act9d0d0/m_avg_drift_loop.mp3","volume":"0.4","id":7,"musicid":0},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_011#2","name2":"avg_npc_053","focus":"2","id":8},{"type":"dialogue","name":"萨卡兹战士","text":"泥岩，他们在追捕剩下的逃犯。","id":9,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/f/f5/Avg_avg_npc_053.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"萨卡兹战士","text":"......但他们本来完全可以让逃犯在这片群山中自生自灭，抓回去，是救了他们的命。","id":10,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/f/f5/Avg_avg_npc_053.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"萨卡兹战士","text":"让人分不清他们是好心还是残忍。","id":11,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/f/f5/Avg_avg_npc_053.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_011#2","name2":"avg_npc_053","focus":"1","id":12},{"type":"dialogue","name":"泥岩","text":"......没有跟来的人都和我们关系不大，但是......","id":13,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/6/6d/Avg_avg_npc_011_2.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"泥岩","text":"尽量避开他们的搜查，我们要在入冬之前离开这里。","id":14,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/6/6d/Avg_avg_npc_011_2.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"泥岩","text":"已经很冷了。","id":15,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/6/6d/Avg_avg_npc_011_2.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_011#2","name2":"avg_npc_053","focus":"2","id":16},{"type":"dialogue","name":"萨卡兹战士","text":"离开这里，去哪儿？","id":17,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/f/f5/Avg_avg_npc_053.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"萨卡兹战士","text":"我们流浪了这么久，到头来呢？永远不会有好结果的。","id":18,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/f/f5/Avg_avg_npc_053.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_011#2","name2":"avg_npc_053","focus":"1","id":19},{"type":"dialogue","name":"泥岩","text":"......那么，我们回家。","id":20,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/6/6d/Avg_avg_npc_011_2.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"泥岩","text":"我们回去，找一片安静的树林，我们在那里生存。","id":21,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/6/6d/Avg_avg_npc_011_2.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_011#2","name2":"avg_npc_053","focus":"2","id":22},{"type":"dialogue","name":"萨卡兹战士","text":"我们要的斗争呢？","id":23,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/f/f5/Avg_avg_npc_053.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_011#2","name2":"avg_npc_053","focus":"1","id":24},{"type":"dialogue","name":"泥岩","text":"......先暂且......活下去。","id":25,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/6/6d/Avg_avg_npc_011_2.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"泥岩","text":"活下去，只是为了活下去，我们就在和这片大地抗争。","id":26,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/6/6d/Avg_avg_npc_011_2.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_067","name2":"avg_npc_011#2","focus":"1","id":27},{"type":"dialogue","name":"武装的感染者","text":"......我们要去哪儿？回家？什么家？","id":28,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/d/d7/Avg_avg_npc_067.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_067","name2":"avg_npc_011#2","focus":"2","id":29},{"type":"dialogue","name":"泥岩","text":"——卡兹戴尔。","id":30,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/6/6d/Avg_avg_npc_011_2.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_067","name2":"avg_npc_011#2","focus":"1","id":31},{"type":"dialogue","name":"武装的感染者","text":"啊......","id":32,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/d/d7/Avg_avg_npc_067.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"武装的感染者","text":"但我们呢？我们不是萨卡兹，那里......","id":33,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/d/d7/Avg_avg_npc_067.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_011#2","id":34},{"type":"dialogue","name":"泥岩","text":"你们，是萨卡兹的同伴。","id":35,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/6/6d/Avg_avg_npc_011_2.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"泥岩","text":"卡兹戴尔之外的地方也许容不下萨卡兹，但卡兹戴尔，容得下你们。","id":36,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/6/6d/Avg_avg_npc_011_2.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"泥岩","text":"虽然这并不是因为宽容，而是因为那里早已......一无所有。","id":37,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/6/6d/Avg_avg_npc_011_2.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"泥岩","text":"卡兹戴尔......不是一座城的名字，也不能算是国家的名称，严格来说，卡兹戴尔只是一个地区。","id":38,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/6/6d/Avg_avg_npc_011_2.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"泥岩","text":"一片不被允许建立家园的流亡者们的土地。","id":39,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/6/6d/Avg_avg_npc_011_2.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"泥岩","text":"那里......是所有无家可归之人的归宿。是所有无根之人的归宿。","id":40,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/6/6d/Avg_avg_npc_011_2.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"泥岩","text":"是你们的归宿。","id":41,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/6/6d/Avg_avg_npc_011_2.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_067","id":42},{"type":"dialogue","name":"武装的感染者","text":"......谢谢。","id":43,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/d/d7/Avg_avg_npc_067.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"武装的感染者","text":"也许在那个遍地都是萨卡兹感染者的卡兹戴尔，我们反而能安安稳稳地生活下去吧......","id":44,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/d/d7/Avg_avg_npc_067.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_067","name2":"avg_npc_053","focus":"2","id":45},{"type":"dialogue","name":"萨卡兹战士","text":"莱塔尼亚对感染者的温和态度终归只是血统和源石技艺普及的副产物，并不代表他们真的愿意接纳你们。","id":46,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/f/f5/Avg_avg_npc_053.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"萨卡兹战士","text":"撕下游刃有余的面具之后，第一个遭到排斥的，还是感染者。","id":47,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/f/f5/Avg_avg_npc_053.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_067","name2":"avg_npc_053","focus":"1","id":48},{"type":"dialogue","name":"武装的感染者","text":"......不光是矿石病，这个繁荣的国家已经遗忘了那些真正悲惨的角落。","id":49,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/d/d7/Avg_avg_npc_067.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"武装的感染者","text":"沃伦姆德这样的悲剧......不过是贵族们怄气的幌子，是银行家和宫廷艺术家们茶余饭后的话题。","id":50,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/d/d7/Avg_avg_npc_067.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"武装的感染者","text":"我们......不能接受。也不想接受。","id":51,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/d/d7/Avg_avg_npc_067.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"武装的感染者","text":"离开就离开吧，我们去卡兹戴尔，去你们的故乡看看。","id":52,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/d/d7/Avg_avg_npc_067.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_067","name2":"avg_npc_011#2","focus":"2","id":53},{"type":"dialogue","name":"泥岩","text":"......嗯。","id":54,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/6/6d/Avg_avg_npc_011_2.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_011#2","name2":"avg_npc_053","focus":"2","id":55},{"type":"dialogue","name":"萨卡兹战士","text":"莱塔尼亚会不会找我们麻烦？","id":56,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/f/f5/Avg_avg_npc_053.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_011#2","name2":"avg_npc_053","focus":"1","id":57},{"type":"dialogue","name":"泥岩","text":"也许吧......无论前因后果如何，一批萨卡兹感染者出现在了一座被毁的城镇，我们会成为罪魁祸首。","id":58,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/6/6d/Avg_avg_npc_011_2.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_067","name2":"avg_npc_011#2","focus":"1","id":59},{"type":"dialogue","name":"武装的感染者","text":"塞弗林知道真相，他难道会栽赃给我们......？","id":60,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/d/d7/Avg_avg_npc_067.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_067","name2":"avg_npc_011#2","focus":"2","id":61},{"type":"dialogue","name":"泥岩","text":"他会的。","id":62,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/6/6d/Avg_avg_npc_011_2.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_067","name2":"avg_npc_011#2","focus":"1","id":63},{"type":"dialogue","name":"武装的感染者","text":".......","id":64,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/d/d7/Avg_avg_npc_067.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_067","name2":"avg_npc_011#2","focus":"2","id":65},{"type":"dialogue","name":"泥岩","text":"......这只是他的行事方式......根据他知道的情报，做出对城镇损害最小的判断。","id":66,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/6/6d/Avg_avg_npc_011_2.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_067","name2":"avg_npc_011#2","focus":"1","id":67},{"type":"dialogue","name":"武装的感染者","text":"那我们必须得快点离开这里，不然的话，我们会遭到莱塔尼亚官方的通缉。","id":68,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/d/d7/Avg_avg_npc_067.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_067","name2":"avg_npc_011#2","focus":"2","id":69},{"type":"dialogue","name":"泥岩","text":"嗯，所以才需要尽早规划路线......啊......","id":70,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/6/6d/Avg_avg_npc_011_2.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_011#2","id":71},{"type":"dialogue","name":"泥岩","text":"抱歉，等我一会，我还要去个地方......","id":72,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/6/6d/Avg_avg_npc_011_2.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"泥岩","text":"一会就好。","id":73,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/6/6d/Avg_avg_npc_011_2.png"},{"type":"stopmusic","fadetime":"3","id":74},{"type":"dialog","id":75},{"type":"character","id":76},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":77},{"type":"background","image":"https://prts.wiki/images/0/02/Avg_bg_bg_ltruins.png","screenadapt":"coverall","id":78},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":79},{"type":"playmusic","intro":"$loneliness_intro","key":"https://static.prts.wiki/music/music/static/m_avg/m_avg_loneliness_loop.mp3","volume":"0.4","id":80,"musicid":1},{"type":"character","name":"char_367_swllow_1#3","id":81},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_gen_walk_n","volume":"0.4","id":82},{"type":"dialogue","name":"灰喉","text":"......","id":83,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/e/e0/Avg_char_367_swllow_3.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_345_folnic_1#4","id":84},{"type":"dialogue","name":"亚叶","text":"你在这里。","id":85,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/2/22/Avg_char_345_folnic_4.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_367_swllow_1","id":86},{"type":"dialogue","name":"灰喉","text":"亚叶干员......","id":87,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/d/da/Avg_char_367_swllow_1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_345_folnic_1#4","id":88},{"type":"dialogue","name":"亚叶","text":"不，不用起身，我不会靠你太近的。","id":89,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/2/22/Avg_char_345_folnic_4.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"亚叶","text":"......你在等人，对吧？","id":90,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/2/22/Avg_char_345_folnic_4.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_367_swllow_1","id":91},{"type":"dialogue","name":"灰喉","text":"嗯。","id":92,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/d/da/Avg_char_367_swllow_1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_345_folnic_1#4","id":93},{"type":"dialogue","name":"亚叶","text":"整合运动事件发生的时候我并不在罗德岛本舰......你似乎，变了不少。","id":94,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/2/22/Avg_char_345_folnic_4.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"亚叶","text":"和传闻中相比，给人的感觉大不一样。","id":95,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/2/22/Avg_char_345_folnic_4.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_367_swllow_1","id":96},{"type":"dialogue","name":"灰喉","text":"传闻？","id":97,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/d/da/Avg_char_367_swllow_1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_345_folnic_1#4","id":98},{"type":"dialogue","name":"亚叶","text":"听说你和一位精英干员并肩作战，在龙门解决了很多事情。","id":99,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/2/22/Avg_char_345_folnic_4.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_367_swllow_1#3","id":100},{"type":"dialogue","name":"灰喉","text":"......只是一只到处撒血的鲁莽大猫。","id":101,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/e/e0/Avg_char_367_swllow_3.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"灰喉","text":"我们也没能......解决任何事情。","id":102,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/e/e0/Avg_char_367_swllow_3.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_345_folnic_1#4","id":103},{"type":"dialogue","name":"亚叶","text":"......谢谢。","id":104,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/2/22/Avg_char_345_folnic_4.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"亚叶","text":"我要再说一次谢谢，如果没有你和小丽萨在，我不知道事情会变成什么样。","id":105,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/2/22/Avg_char_345_folnic_4.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_367_swllow_1#3","id":106},{"type":"dialogue","name":"灰喉","text":"......","id":107,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/e/e0/Avg_char_367_swllow_3.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_345_folnic_1#4","id":108},{"type":"dialogue","name":"亚叶","text":"罗德岛也好，塞弗林也好，哪怕是那个整合运动也好，明明没有人希望事情变成这一步......","id":109,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/2/22/Avg_char_345_folnic_4.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"亚叶","text":"好像所有人都在阻拦着惨剧发生，但它依旧势不可挡。","id":110,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/2/22/Avg_char_345_folnic_4.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"亚叶","text":"安托她......她......","id":111,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/2/22/Avg_char_345_folnic_4.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_367_swllow_1","id":112},{"type":"dialogue","name":"灰喉","text":"不用勉强自己感慨什么，事情已经过去了。","id":113,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/d/da/Avg_char_367_swllow_1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_367_swllow_1#3","id":114},{"type":"dialogue","name":"灰喉","text":"只愿逝者安息。","id":115,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/e/e0/Avg_char_367_swllow_3.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_345_folnic_1#4","id":116},{"type":"dialogue","name":"亚叶","text":"......我们没能将凶手绳之于法，不仅如此，我们甚至没能保护好安托保护过的这座城镇。","id":117,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/2/22/Avg_char_345_folnic_4.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"亚叶","text":"安托她会怪我的吧。","id":118,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/2/22/Avg_char_345_folnic_4.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_367_swllow_1","id":119},{"type":"dialogue","name":"灰喉","text":"只有你会怪罪你自己，安托小姐是个开朗的人。","id":120,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/d/da/Avg_char_367_swllow_1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"灰喉","text":"是啊，我想她会拍拍你的肩膀，然后陪你喝到烂醉。","id":121,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/d/da/Avg_char_367_swllow_1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_345_folnic_1#2","id":122},{"type":"dialogue","name":"亚叶","text":"呵呵......也是啦，原来你们很熟？","id":123,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/8/82/Avg_char_345_folnic_2.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_367_swllow_1","id":124},{"type":"dialogue","name":"灰喉","text":"我和那个陪她喝到烂醉的“精英干员”很熟。","id":125,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/d/da/Avg_char_367_swllow_1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_367_swllow_1","id":126},{"type":"dialogue","name":"灰喉","text":"......放弃追究这一切的人，不止我们。","id":127,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/d/da/Avg_char_367_swllow_1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":128},{"type":"character","id":129},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_gen_walk_n","volume":"0.4","id":130},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_011#2","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":131},{"type":"delay","time":"2","id":132},{"type":"dialogue","name":"泥岩","text":"......","id":133,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/6/6d/Avg_avg_npc_011_2.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_367_swllow_1","id":134},{"type":"dialogue","name":"灰喉","text":"你果然来了。","id":135,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/d/da/Avg_char_367_swllow_1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_367_swllow_1","name2":"avg_npc_011#2","focus":"2","id":136},{"type":"dialogue","name":"泥岩","text":"这是，新摘的野花......","id":137,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/6/6d/Avg_avg_npc_011_2.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_367_swllow_1","name2":"avg_npc_011#2","focus":"1","id":138},{"type":"dialogue","name":"灰喉","text":"你应该清楚眼下的状况，清扫任务已经接近尾声，而罗德岛近期就会离开这里，试着联络资源调度进行援助。","id":139,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/d/da/Avg_char_367_swllow_1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"灰喉","text":"但到那时候......","id":140,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/d/da/Avg_char_367_swllow_1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_367_swllow_1","name2":"avg_npc_011#2","focus":"2","id":141},{"type":"dialogue","name":"泥岩","text":"没有人会为我们说话，我知道。","id":142,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/6/6d/Avg_avg_npc_011_2.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"泥岩","text":"......我不会怪塞弗林。他只能这么向贵族们汇报，否则要遭殃的是他们......","id":143,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/6/6d/Avg_avg_npc_011_2.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"泥岩","text":"我们会尽快离开这里，很快。只是，这里还有我们死去的同伴......我不想不辞而别。","id":144,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/6/6d/Avg_avg_npc_011_2.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_345_folnic_1#4","id":145},{"type":"dialogue","name":"亚叶","text":"......八名感染者。","id":146,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/2/22/Avg_char_345_folnic_4.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"亚叶","text":"现在，沃伦姆德死伤的人数，可比“八名”多上几百倍——","id":147,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/2/22/Avg_char_345_folnic_4.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_011#2","id":148},{"type":"dialogue","name":"泥岩","text":"......抱歉。","id":149,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/6/6d/Avg_avg_npc_011_2.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_345_folnic_1#4","id":150},{"type":"dialogue","name":"亚叶","text":"不......这不是你的问题......我没有在责难你。","id":151,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/2/22/Avg_char_345_folnic_4.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"亚叶","text":"我只是在反思，反思到底是什么让事情变成这样。","id":152,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/2/22/Avg_char_345_folnic_4.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"亚叶","text":"我当然知道这片大地可不是做好事有好报这么天真，但我也......很少见过这种，这种自我毁灭。","id":153,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/2/22/Avg_char_345_folnic_4.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"亚叶","text":"被煽动的怒火和复仇欲差点摧毁了一切......连我自己也......","id":154,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/2/22/Avg_char_345_folnic_4.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_367_swllow_1","id":155},{"type":"dialogue","name":"灰喉","text":"你还是在自责。","id":156,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/d/da/Avg_char_367_swllow_1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_345_folnic_1#4","id":157},{"type":"dialogue","name":"亚叶","text":"不......我已经冷静下来了。我只是在想，也许不是“没做好”，而是“做不到”。","id":158,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/2/22/Avg_char_345_folnic_4.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"亚叶","text":"罗德岛一直以来......凯尔希医生教导我的......我做不到。","id":159,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/2/22/Avg_char_345_folnic_4.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_011#2","id":160},{"type":"dialogue","name":"泥岩","text":"——没人做得到。","id":161,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/6/6d/Avg_avg_npc_011_2.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"泥岩","text":"我阻止过他们过激的行径，但一两次阻止并不能浇灭他们复仇的怒火。","id":162,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/6/6d/Avg_avg_npc_011_2.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"泥岩","text":"所以......事情还是变成了这样。","id":163,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/6/6d/Avg_avg_npc_011_2.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_345_folnic_1#4","id":164},{"type":"dialogue","name":"亚叶","text":"......","id":165,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/2/22/Avg_char_345_folnic_4.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_367_swllow_1","name2":"avg_npc_011#2","focus":"1","id":166},{"type":"dialogue","name":"灰喉","text":"你接下来要怎么做？“整合运动”仍旧是大部分人的眼中钉，你应该彻底抛弃这个标志。","id":167,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/d/da/Avg_char_367_swllow_1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_367_swllow_1","name2":"avg_npc_011#2","focus":"2","id":168},{"type":"dialogue","name":"泥岩","text":"你说得对......但“整合运动”并没有消亡，这一消息已经在莱塔尼亚的感染者间传开。","id":169,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/6/6d/Avg_avg_npc_011_2.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"泥岩","text":"抗争的火种延续了下去......尽管它，扭曲变形。而我们也必须稍作喘息。","id":170,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/6/6d/Avg_avg_npc_011_2.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"泥岩","text":"我的队伍里有太多不是战士的人，我不能擅自帮他们决定他们的命运......他们也许，只是想平静地生活。","id":171,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/6/6d/Avg_avg_npc_011_2.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_011#2","name2":"char_345_folnic_1#4","focus":"1","id":172},{"type":"dialogue","name":"泥岩","text":"对了......罗德岛，你们听说过大鲍勃吗？","id":173,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/6/6d/Avg_avg_npc_011_2.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_011#2","name2":"char_345_folnic_1#4","focus":"2","id":174},{"type":"dialogue","name":"亚叶","text":"——没有。","id":175,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/2/22/Avg_char_345_folnic_4.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"亚叶","text":"如果有什么关联的话，我可以去调查档案。","id":176,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/2/22/Avg_char_345_folnic_4.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_011#2","name2":"char_345_folnic_1#4","focus":"1","id":177},{"type":"dialogue","name":"泥岩","text":"不，没有，只是我的一个朋友......","id":178,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/6/6d/Avg_avg_npc_011_2.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_011#2","name2":"char_345_folnic_1#4","focus":"2","id":179},{"type":"dialogue","name":"亚叶","text":"整合运动？还是萨卡兹？","id":180,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/2/22/Avg_char_345_folnic_4.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_011#2","name2":"char_345_folnic_1#4","focus":"1","id":181},{"type":"dialogue","name":"泥岩","text":"——整合运动。他是一个经验丰富的赏金猎人。","id":182,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/6/6d/Avg_avg_npc_011_2.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"泥岩","text":"他们不是战士，所以，他们有理由脱身......他们应当从压迫中喘口气，去哥伦比亚拓荒的队伍里寻找一席之地......","id":183,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/6/6d/Avg_avg_npc_011_2.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"泥岩","text":"啊......想起来了，他们还有啤酒花。","id":184,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/6/6d/Avg_avg_npc_011_2.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_011#2","name2":"char_345_folnic_1#4","focus":"2","id":185},{"type":"dialogue","name":"亚叶","text":"什么？","id":186,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/2/22/Avg_char_345_folnic_4.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_011#2","name2":"char_345_folnic_1#4","focus":"1","id":187},{"type":"dialogue","name":"泥岩","text":"你见过啤酒花吗？那是怎么用的？啤酒是用植物做成的吗？","id":188,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/6/6d/Avg_avg_npc_011_2.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_011#2","name2":"char_345_folnic_1#2","focus":"2","id":189},{"type":"dialogue","name":"亚叶","text":"呃，是种很棒的植物......啤酒的泡沫应该和它有关，啊，好像还能延长防腐——","id":190,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/8/82/Avg_char_345_folnic_2.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"亚叶","text":"——不，我们真的要认真解释这个吗？我不是专业的啊。","id":191,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/8/82/Avg_char_345_folnic_2.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_367_swllow_1#3","id":192},{"type":"dialogue","name":"灰喉","text":"......反正很有用。","id":193,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/e/e0/Avg_char_367_swllow_3.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_011#2","id":194},{"type":"dialogue","name":"泥岩","text":"是这样......真羡慕啊。","id":195,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/6/6d/Avg_avg_npc_011_2.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"泥岩","text":"啤酒花......泡沫......啤酒......","id":196,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/6/6d/Avg_avg_npc_011_2.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_011#2","name2":"char_345_folnic_1#2","focus":"2","id":197},{"type":"dialogue","name":"亚叶","text":"......别想着啤酒出神了，喂。我们好歹也是敌对的。","id":198,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/8/82/Avg_char_345_folnic_2.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_367_swllow_1","name2":"avg_npc_011#2","focus":"1","id":199},{"type":"dialogue","name":"灰喉","text":"我们好歹身份有别。","id":200,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/d/da/Avg_char_367_swllow_1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_011#2","id":201},{"type":"dialogue","name":"泥岩","text":"啊......抱歉。","id":202,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/6/6d/Avg_avg_npc_011_2.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"泥岩","text":"但我们，是战士。萨卡兹们，是战士。","id":203,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/6/6d/Avg_avg_npc_011_2.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_367_swllow_1","name2":"avg_npc_011#2","focus":"1","id":204},{"type":"dialogue","name":"灰喉","text":"不得不说......很难从你的言行里感受到你作为战士的坚决。","id":205,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/d/da/Avg_char_367_swllow_1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_367_swllow_1","name2":"avg_npc_011#2","focus":"2","id":206},{"type":"dialogue","name":"泥岩","text":"我们别无选择。","id":207,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/6/6d/Avg_avg_npc_011_2.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"泥岩","text":"如果我们有什么诉求，有什么需要伸张的信念，有什么必须保护的对象，我们只能战斗。","id":208,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/6/6d/Avg_avg_npc_011_2.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_367_swllow_1","name2":"avg_npc_011#2","focus":"1","id":209},{"type":"dialogue","name":"灰喉","text":"不止有战斗可以解决问题。","id":210,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/d/da/Avg_char_367_swllow_1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_367_swllow_1","name2":"avg_npc_011#2","focus":"2","id":211},{"type":"dialogue","name":"泥岩","text":"那么......我们牺牲的同伴如何是好？靠和平的主张，那些坏人就会把家园和城市为我们准备好吗？","id":212,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/6/6d/Avg_avg_npc_011_2.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"泥岩","text":"不会的。","id":213,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/6/6d/Avg_avg_npc_011_2.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"泥岩","text":"我们......我们只能战斗下去......为了帮助感染者同胞们。","id":214,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/6/6d/Avg_avg_npc_011_2.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_011#2","name2":"char_345_folnic_1#4","focus":"2","id":215},{"type":"dialogue","name":"亚叶","text":"......“感染者同胞”。","id":216,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/2/22/Avg_char_345_folnic_4.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"亚叶","text":"你们能去哪里？","id":217,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/2/22/Avg_char_345_folnic_4.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_011#2","name2":"char_345_folnic_1#4","focus":"1","id":218},{"type":"dialogue","name":"泥岩","text":"卡兹戴尔。","id":219,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/6/6d/Avg_avg_npc_011_2.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_011#2","name2":"char_345_folnic_1#3","focus":"2","id":220},{"type":"dialogue","name":"亚叶","text":"卡兹戴尔，那可不是个好地方。","id":221,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/e/e9/Avg_char_345_folnic_3.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_011#2","name2":"char_345_folnic_1#3","focus":"1","id":222},{"type":"dialogue","name":"泥岩","text":"我们也不是什么好伙计，罗德岛。","id":223,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/6/6d/Avg_avg_npc_011_2.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"泥岩","text":"真正的“好地方”，是容不下我们的。","id":224,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/6/6d/Avg_avg_npc_011_2.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_367_swllow_1","name2":"avg_npc_011#2","focus":"1","id":225},{"type":"dialogue","name":"灰喉","text":"你有另一个选择，泥岩。","id":226,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/d/da/Avg_char_367_swllow_1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_011#2","id":227},{"type":"dialogue","name":"泥岩","text":"......现在，还不行。","id":228,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/6/6d/Avg_avg_npc_011_2.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"泥岩","text":"这些莱塔尼亚人，这些萨卡兹，他们都有自己的想法。","id":229,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/6/6d/Avg_avg_npc_011_2.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"泥岩","text":"怨愤并没有消去，没有什么可以让他们轻易相信他人，只有团结在一起活下去的意志，才把他们凝聚在一起。仅此而已。","id":230,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/6/6d/Avg_avg_npc_011_2.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_367_swllow_1","name2":"avg_npc_011#2","focus":"1","id":231},{"type":"dialogue","name":"灰喉","text":"......很遗憾。","id":232,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/d/da/Avg_char_367_swllow_1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_367_swllow_1","name2":"avg_npc_011#2","focus":"2","id":233},{"type":"dialogue","name":"泥岩","text":"不，罗德岛的燕子，也许我们还会再见的......为了感染者而战的人。","id":234,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/6/6d/Avg_avg_npc_011_2.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_367_swllow_1","name2":"avg_npc_011#2","focus":"1","id":235},{"type":"dialogue","name":"灰喉","text":"......你不是第一个这么称呼我的整合运动。","id":236,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/d/da/Avg_char_367_swllow_1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_367_swllow_1","name2":"avg_npc_011#2","focus":"2","id":237},{"type":"dialogue","name":"泥岩","text":"......是这样。","id":238,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/6/6d/Avg_avg_npc_011_2.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"泥岩","text":"我离开这里后，我们，依旧是敌人。","id":239,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/6/6d/Avg_avg_npc_011_2.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"泥岩","text":"否则莱塔尼亚会怀疑你们，你们无法顺利脱身。","id":240,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/6/6d/Avg_avg_npc_011_2.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_011#2","id":241},{"type":"dialogue","name":"泥岩","text":"所以......就不要和敌人关系太过密切了。","id":242,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/6/6d/Avg_avg_npc_011_2.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"泥岩","text":"我只是来献一束花，既然花已经带到，我......也该走了。","id":243,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/6/6d/Avg_avg_npc_011_2.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"泥岩","text":"祝你们好运。","id":244,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/6/6d/Avg_avg_npc_011_2.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":245},{"type":"character","id":246},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_gen_walk_n","volume":"0.4","id":247},{"type":"delay","time":"2","id":248},{"type":"character","name":"char_345_folnic_1#4","id":249},{"type":"dialogue","name":"亚叶","text":"......","id":250,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/2/22/Avg_char_345_folnic_4.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_367_swllow_1","name2":"char_345_folnic_1#4","focus":"1","id":251},{"type":"dialogue","name":"灰喉","text":"如果你还有什么话想说，趁现在。","id":252,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/d/da/Avg_char_367_swllow_1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_367_swllow_1","name2":"char_345_folnic_1#4","focus":"2","id":253},{"type":"dialogue","name":"亚叶","text":"......没什么。","id":254,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/2/22/Avg_char_345_folnic_4.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"亚叶","text":"只是，就像做了一个噩梦，看他走远之后，我突然觉得，梦醒了。","id":255,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/2/22/Avg_char_345_folnic_4.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"亚叶","text":"这样就......结束了。","id":256,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/2/22/Avg_char_345_folnic_4.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_367_swllow_1","name2":"char_345_folnic_1#4","focus":"1","id":257},{"type":"dialogue","name":"灰喉","text":"我不是很会安慰人，不过——","id":258,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/d/da/Avg_char_367_swllow_1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_367_swllow_1","name2":"char_345_folnic_1#4","focus":"2","id":259},{"type":"dialogue","name":"亚叶","text":"我，其实知道你的事情，不该是你来安慰我的......对不起。","id":260,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/2/22/Avg_char_345_folnic_4.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_367_swllow_1","name2":"char_345_folnic_1#4","focus":"1","id":261},{"type":"dialogue","name":"灰喉","text":"......我们只能让悲痛结束......这不是什么好事，这是妥协，为了继续活下去的妥协。","id":262,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/d/da/Avg_char_367_swllow_1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_367_swllow_1","name2":"char_345_folnic_1#4","focus":"2","id":263},{"type":"dialogue","name":"亚叶","text":"你花了多久接受这种心情？","id":264,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/2/22/Avg_char_345_folnic_4.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_367_swllow_1","name2":"char_345_folnic_1#4","focus":"1","id":265},{"type":"dialogue","name":"灰喉","text":"......很久。久到足以失去更多的东西。","id":266,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/d/da/Avg_char_367_swllow_1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_367_swllow_1","name2":"char_345_folnic_1#4","focus":"2","id":267},{"type":"dialogue","name":"亚叶","text":"......","id":268,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/2/22/Avg_char_345_folnic_4.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_367_swllow_1","name2":"char_345_folnic_1#4","focus":"1","id":269},{"type":"dialogue","name":"灰喉","text":"......","id":270,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/d/da/Avg_char_367_swllow_1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"灰喉","text":"......接下来？","id":271,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/d/da/Avg_char_367_swllow_1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_367_swllow_1","name2":"char_345_folnic_1#2","focus":"2","id":272},{"type":"dialogue","name":"亚叶","text":"回罗德岛去。","id":273,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/8/82/Avg_char_345_folnic_2.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"亚叶","text":"我们......带安托回家。","id":274,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/8/82/Avg_char_345_folnic_2.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":275},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"3","block":"true","id":276},{"type":"character","id":277},{"type":"image","id":278}],"characters":["萨卡兹战士","泥岩","武装的感染者","灰喉","亚叶"]}